This is a polyrepo containing several subprojects around stock-screening. The main project is called FINS, full path: /r/priv/stock-screener/

The sqlite3 database is located at  ~/.fins/db/symbols.db

Entities are persited to  ~/.fins/persistence/ in json format. 

Before executing anything, make sure to be in the project root /r/priv/stock-screener/

